document_data.History:
Pendar assumed the throne of the High King in the {{YearlinkName|738}}, following the death of his father.

In the [[745 DR|seventh year of his reign]], the first raid in a centuries-long practice by the [[fire giant]]s of [[Tuern]] occurred when their [[longship]]s arrived in [[Gundarlun]] and sacked the city of [[Gundbarg]].{{Cite dragon/362/Grand History of the Realms: The Moonshaes|27}}

Pendar ruled for eleven years before being killed by [[wolves]] in the {{YearlinkName|749}}.
